532
00:41:59,815 --> 00:42:01,651
Hoşgeldiniz.

533
00:42:01,817 --> 00:42:03,527
Memnun olduk, gerçekten.

534
00:42:06,948 --> 00:42:08,699
Prens...

535
00:42:09,784 --> 00:42:13,496
